&lt;h2 id="prevention-tips"&gt;Prevention Tips&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Always set timeouts on HTTP requests — never rely on the default 120 seconds.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;AbortController&lt;/code&gt; with &lt;code&gt;fetch()&lt;/code&gt; for modern timeout handling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use keep-alive agents for services with repeated connections.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement retry logic with exponential backoff for transient network failures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor socket timeout events to identify slow endpoints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
